    "is_free": false,
    "description": "为终极塔防猛攻做好准备。在这场史诗般的科幻冒险中建造、部署、研究和升级你的防御工事。 <br><br>设定在 100 年后的未来，与太阳系内的跨维度血肉战斗，保卫地球殖民地免遭彻底毁灭。 <br><br>节奏是稳定的，但赌注很高，因为无情的部落聚集在一起，试图超越你的移动指挥中心。与传统的 TD 游戏不同，您将严重依赖微观管理基于动态动作的能力。随着您在战役空袭中的深入推进，蓄力攻击、防御工事墙和战术无人机将变得越来越重要，战略性地部署它们将变得至关重要。 <br><br>错误不会逍遥法外，所以要保持冷静，从错误中吸取教训，然后再继续战斗。没有痛苦就没有收获！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>测试您的技能的活动</strong></h2><br>战场是一片无情的风景，每一秒都很重要。初学者会在正常模式下得到宽恕，而老手将被吸引到困难的挑战中。当你准备好时，是时候在噩梦和生存中考验你的技能了。<br><br>你能阻止部落多久？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223590/extras/25b5a8ddf595e0d1f6298805fa02d6c0.poster.avif?t=1770715102\" width=600 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223590/extras/25b5a8ddf595e0d1f6298805fa02d6c0.webm?t=1770715102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223590/extras/25b5a8ddf595e0d1f6298805fa02d6c0.mp4?t=1770715102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>精美插图的环境和图形</strong></h2><br>2112TD 的艺术风格建立在对 RTS 黄金时代的怀旧之上，向命令与征服、星际争霸等游戏致敬。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223590/extras/af3d61ad8d0e2b1ed16ba2afe9c30f3f.poster.avif?t=1770715102\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223590/extras/af3d61ad8d0e2b1ed16ba2afe9c30f3f.webm?t=1770715102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223590/extras/af3d61ad8d0e2b1ed16ba2afe9c30f3f.mp4?t=1770715102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>燃烧、爆炸和消除</strong></h2><br>部署机枪、火焰喷射器、大炮和等离子炮塔来摧毁你的敌人。将你的塔升级到他们的实验阶段，包含强大的火力和蓄力攻击。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223590/extras/d4f2b286c5fd3900a28ca8ea85bd3691.poster.avif?t=1770715102\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223590/extras/d4f2b286c5fd3900a28ca8ea85bd3691.webm?t=1770715102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223590/extras/d4f2b286c5fd3900a28ca8ea85bd3691.mp4?t=1770715102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>来自天上的死亡</strong></h2><br>当情况变得过于棘手时，您将依赖空中支援。空袭和战术无人机提供了强大的 BOOM 和防御能力。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223590/extras/d5d4f1fb94a977680a300be25d784f6c.poster.avif?t=1770715102\" width=600 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223590/extras/d5d4f1fb94a977680a300be25d784f6c.webm?t=1770715102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2223590/extras/d5d4f1fb94a977680a300be25d784f6c.mp4?t=1770715102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>研究胜利</strong></h2><br>地球的蛋头们正在不知疲倦地工作，以在对抗新敌人时占上风。随着你的进步解锁新的能力和武器。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>发现并统治 </strong></h2><br>他们称之为士兵词典。战术数据库在战场上收集有关您的武器库和敌人的数据。一定要经常检查它，因为它对你战胜成群结队至关重要。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成就和战斗统计</strong></h2><br>在战场上表现出色的指挥官将解锁成就，作为他们在与入侵者斗争中的贡献的奖励。 <br><br><br><strong>指挥官还等什么？必须铲除血肉之躯！</strong>",
